{
  "video_id": "yjYrxcGSWX4",
  "title": "A powerful way to unleash your natural creativity | Tim Harford",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13640.0,
      "end_time": 17856.0,
      "text": "\"To do two things at once is to do neither.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17880.0,
      "end_time": 20656.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a great smackdown of multitasking, isn&#39;t it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20680.0,
      "end_time": 24216.0,
      "text": "often attributed to the Roman writer Publilius Syrus,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24240.0,
      "end_time": 27919.0,
      "text": "although you know how these things are, he probably never said it."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 28640.0,
      "end_time": 31936.0,
      "text": "What I&#39;m interested in, though, is -- is it true?"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 31960.0,
      "end_time": 35656.0,
      "text": "I mean, it&#39;s obviously true for emailing at the dinner table"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 35680.0,
      "end_time": 41560.0,
      "text": "or texting while driving or possibly for live tweeting at TED Talk, as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 41800.0,
      "end_time": 45775.0,
      "text": "But I&#39;d like to argue that for an important kind of activity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 45800.0,
      "end_time": 48616.0,
      "text": "doing two things at once -- or three or even four --"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 48640.0,
      "end_time": 51776.0,
      "text": "is exactly what we should be aiming for."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 51800.0,
      "end_time": 54535.0,
      "text": "Look no further than Albert Einstein."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 54560.0,
      "end_time": 58736.0,
      "text": "In 1905, he published four remarkable scientific papers."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 58760.0,
      "end_time": 60696.0,
      "text": "One of them was on Brownian motion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 60720.0,
      "end_time": 64560.0,
      "text": "it provided empirical evidence that atoms exist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 64800.0,
      "end_time": 68295.0,
      "text": "and it laid out the basic mathematics behind most of financial economics."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 68320.0,
      "end_time": 71175.0,
      "text": "Another one was on the theory of special relativity."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 71200.0,
      "end_time": 73896.0,
      "text": "Another one was on the photoelectric effect,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 73920.0,
      "end_time": 76280.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s why solar panels work, it&#39;s a nice one."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 77280.0,
      "end_time": 79496.0,
      "text": "Gave him the Nobel prize for that one."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 79520.0,
      "end_time": 82655.0,
      "text": "And the fourth introduced an equation you might have heard of:"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 82680.0,
      "end_time": 84976.0,
      "text": "E equals mc squared."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 85000.0,
      "end_time": 88576.0,
      "text": "So, tell me again how you shouldn&#39;t do several things at once."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 88600.0,
      "end_time": 91976.0,
      "text": "Now, obviously, working simultaneously"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 92000.0,
      "end_time": 95896.0,
      "text": "on Brownian motion, special relativity and the photoelectric effect --"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 95920.0,
      "end_time": 98456.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s not exactly the same kind of multitasking"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 98480.0,
      "end_time": 101960.0,
      "text": "as Snapchatting while you&#39;re watching \"Westworld.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 101120.0,
      "end_time": 102576.0,
      "text": "Very different."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 102600.0,
      "end_time": 106256.0,
      "text": "And Einstein, yeah, well, Einstein&#39;s -- he&#39;s Einstein,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 106280.0,
      "end_time": 107840.0,
      "text": "he&#39;s one of a kind, he&#39;s unique."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 108680.0,
      "end_time": 111896.0,
      "text": "But the pattern of behavior that Einstein was demonstrating,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 111920.0,
      "end_time": 114496.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s not unique at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 114520.0,
      "end_time": 117816.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s very common among highly creative people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 117840.0,
      "end_time": 120496.0,
      "text": "both artists and scientists,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 120520.0,
      "end_time": 122216.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;d like to give it a name:"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 122240.0,
      "end_time": 125390.0,
      "text": "slow-motion multitasking."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 126160.0,
      "end_time": 130536.0,
      "text": "Slow-motion multitasking feels like a counterintuitive idea."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 130560.0,
      "end_time": 132160.0,
      "text": "What I&#39;m describing here"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 132400.0,
      "end_time": 135736.0,
      "text": "is having multiple projects on the go at the same time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 135760.0,
      "end_time": 140375.0,
      "text": "and you move backwards and forwards between topics as the mood takes you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 140400.0,
      "end_time": 142376.0,
      "text": "or as the situation demands."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 142400.0,
      "end_time": 144776.0,
      "text": "But the reason it seems counterintuitive"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 144800.0,
      "end_time": 148976.0,
      "text": "is because we&#39;re used to lapsing into multitasking out of desperation."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 149000.0,
      "end_time": 151520.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re in a hurry, we want to do everything at once."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 152720.0,
      "end_time": 156856.0,
      "text": "If we were willing to slow multitasking down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 156880.0,
      "end_time": 160400.0,
      "text": "we might find that it works quite brilliantly."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 161720.0,
      "end_time": 166416.0,
      "text": "Sixty years ago, a young psychologist by the name of Bernice Eiduson"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 166440.0,
      "end_time": 168416.0,
      "text": "began a long research project"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 168440.0,
      "end_time": 171536.0,
      "text": "into the personalities and the working habits"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 171560.0,
      "end_time": 174256.0,
      "text": "of 40 leading scientists."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 174280.0,
      "end_time": 175936.0,
      "text": "Einstein was already dead,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 175960.0,
      "end_time": 178896.0,
      "text": "but four of her subjects won Nobel prizes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 178920.0,
      "end_time": 181679.0,
      "text": "including Linus Pauling and Richard Feynman."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 182560.0,
      "end_time": 184176.0,
      "text": "The research went on for decades,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 184200.0,
      "end_time": 188456.0,
      "text": "in fact, it continued even after professor Eiduson herself had died."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 188480.0,
      "end_time": 190976.0,
      "text": "And one of the questions that it answered"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 191000.0,
      "end_time": 197536.0,
      "text": "was, \"How is it that some scientists are able to go on producing important work"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 197560.0,
      "end_time": 199656.0,
      "text": "right through their lives?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 199680.0,
      "end_time": 201336.0,
      "text": "What is it about these people?"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 201360.0,
      "end_time": 205256.0,
      "text": "Is it their personality, is it their skill set,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 205280.0,
      "end_time": 207400.0,
      "text": "their daily routines, what?"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 208400.0,
      "end_time": 213400.0,
      "text": "Well, a pattern that emerged was clear, and I think to some people surprising."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 214520.0,
      "end_time": 219336.0,
      "text": "The top scientists kept changing the subject."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 219360.0,
      "end_time": 222960.0,
      "text": "They would shift topics repeatedly"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 222120.0,
      "end_time": 226136.0,
      "text": "during their first 100 published research papers."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 226160.0,
      "end_time": 228335.0,
      "text": "Do you want to guess how often?"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 228360.0,
      "end_time": 230960.0,
      "text": "Three times?"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 230120.0,
      "end_time": 231320.0,
      "text": "Five times?"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 232280.0,
      "end_time": 236416.0,
      "text": "No. On average, the most enduringly creative scientists"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 236440.0,
      "end_time": 242680.0,
      "text": "switched topics 43 times in their first 100 research papers."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 243840.0,
      "end_time": 248616.0,
      "text": "Seems that the secret to creativity is multitasking"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 248640.0,
      "end_time": 249839.0,
      "text": "in slow motion."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 251400.0,
      "end_time": 255176.0,
      "text": "Eiduson&#39;s research suggests we need to reclaim multitasking"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 255200.0,
      "end_time": 258296.0,
      "text": "and remind ourselves how powerful it can be."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 258320.0,
      "end_time": 260656.0,
      "text": "And she&#39;s not the only person to have found this."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 260680.0,
      "end_time": 261896.0,
      "text": "Different researchers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 261920.00000000003,
      "end_time": 265496.0,
      "text": "using different methods to study different highly creative people"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 265520.0,
      "end_time": 269135.0,
      "text": "have found that very often they have multiple projects in progress"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 269160.0,
      "end_time": 270375.0,
      "text": "at the same time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 270399.0,
      "end_time": 275136.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;re also far more likely than most of us to have serious hobbies."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 275160.0,
      "end_time": 279600.0,
      "text": "Slow-motion multitasking among creative people is ubiquitous."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 280480.0,
      "end_time": 281680.0,
      "text": "So, why?"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 283160.0,
      "end_time": 284736.0,
      "text": "I think there are three reasons."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 284760.0,
      "end_time": 287296.0,
      "text": "And the first is the simplest."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 287320.0,
      "end_time": 291576.0,
      "text": "Creativity often comes when you take an idea from its original context"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 291600.0,
      "end_time": 293960.0,
      "text": "and you move it somewhere else."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 293120.0,
      "end_time": 294856.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s easier to think outside the box"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 294880.0,
      "end_time": 298000.0,
      "text": "if you spend your time clambering from one box into another."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 298840.0,
      "end_time": 303880.0,
      "text": "For an example of this, consider the original eureka moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 304520.0,
      "end_time": 308176.0,
      "text": "Archimedes -- he&#39;s wrestling with a difficult problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 308200.0,
      "end_time": 310695.0,
      "text": "And he realizes, in a flash,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 310720.0,
      "end_time": 314376.0,
      "text": "he can solve it, using the displacement of water."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 314400.0,
      "end_time": 316960.0,
      "text": "And if you believe the story,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 316120.0,
      "end_time": 319616.0,
      "text": "this idea comes to him as he&#39;s taking a bath,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 319640.0,
      "end_time": 324816.0,
      "text": "lowering himself in, and he&#39;s watching the water level rise and fall."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 324840.0,
      "end_time": 329455.0,
      "text": "And if solving a problem while having a bath isn&#39;t multitasking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 329480.0,
      "end_time": 330880.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t know what is."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 332200.0,
      "end_time": 334616.0,
      "text": "The second reason that multitasking can work"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 334640.0,
      "end_time": 338150.0,
      "text": "is that learning to do one thing well"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 338400.0,
      "end_time": 340576.0,
      "text": "can often help you do something else."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 340600.0,
      "end_time": 343576.0,
      "text": "Any athlete can tell you about the benefits of cross-training."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 343600.0,
      "end_time": 346160.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s possible to cross-train your mind, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 347400.0,
      "end_time": 352496.0,
      "text": "A few years ago, researchers took 18 randomly chosen medical students"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 352520.0,
      "end_time": 357656.0,
      "text": "and they enrolled them in a course at the Philadelphia Museum of Art,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 357680.0,
      "end_time": 362456.0,
      "text": "where they learned to criticize and analyze works of visual art."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 362480.0,
      "end_time": 364336.0,
      "text": "And at the end of the course,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 364360.0,
      "end_time": 366976.0,
      "text": "these students were compared with a control group"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 367000.0,
      "end_time": 368576.0,
      "text": "of their fellow medical students."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 368600.0,
      "end_time": 371336.0,
      "text": "And the ones who had taken the art course"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 371360.0,
      "end_time": 375176.0,
      "text": "had become substantially better at performing tasks"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 375200.0,
      "end_time": 380560.0,
      "text": "such as diagnosing diseases of the eye by analyzing photographs."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 380800.0,
      "end_time": 382776.0,
      "text": "They&#39;d become better eye doctors."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 382800.0,
      "end_time": 385816.0,
      "text": "So if we want to become better at what we do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 385840.0,
      "end_time": 388376.0,
      "text": "maybe we should spend some time doing something else,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 388400.0,
      "end_time": 392135.0,
      "text": "even if the two fields appear to be as completely distinct"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 392160.0,
      "end_time": 395320.0,
      "text": "as ophthalmology and the history of art."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 396360.0,
      "end_time": 399176.0,
      "text": "And if you&#39;d like an example of this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 399200.0,
      "end_time": 402536.0,
      "text": "should we go for a less intimidating example than Einstein? OK."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 402560.0,
      "end_time": 406896.0,
      "text": "Michael Crichton, creator of \"Jurassic Park\" and \"E.R.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 406920.0,
      "end_time": 410296.0,
      "text": "So in the 1970s, he originally trained as a doctor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 410320.0,
      "end_time": 412856.0,
      "text": "but then he wrote novels"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 412880.0,
      "end_time": 416135.0,
      "text": "and he directed the original \"Westworld\" movie."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 416160.0,
      "end_time": 418296.0,
      "text": "But also, and this is less well-known,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 418320.0,
      "end_time": 420560.0,
      "text": "he also wrote nonfiction books,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 420800.0,
      "end_time": 423280.0,
      "text": "about art, about medicine, about computer programming."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 424480.0,
      "end_time": 429536.0,
      "text": "So in 1995, he enjoyed the fruits of all this variety"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 429560.0,
      "end_time": 433760.0,
      "text": "by penning the world&#39;s most commercially successful book."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 434440.0,
      "end_time": 438760.0,
      "text": "And the world&#39;s most commercially successful TV series."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 439680.0,
      "end_time": 443360.0,
      "text": "And the world&#39;s most commercially successful movie."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 444280.0,
      "end_time": 447159.0,
      "text": "In 1996, he did it all over again."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 449240.0,
      "end_time": 450896.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a third reason"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 450920.0,
      "end_time": 455216.0,
      "text": "why slow-motion multitasking can help us solve problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 455240.0,
      "end_time": 458936.0,
      "text": "It can provide assistance when we&#39;re stuck."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 458960.0,
      "end_time": 461176.0,
      "text": "This can&#39;t happen in an instant."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 461200.0,
      "end_time": 464575.0,
      "text": "So, imagine that feeling of working on a crossword puzzle"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 464600.0,
      "end_time": 466376.0,
      "text": "and you can&#39;t figure out the answer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 466400.0,
      "end_time": 470575.0,
      "text": "and the reason you can&#39;t is because the wrong answer is stuck in your head."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 470600.0,
      "end_time": 473136.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s very easy -- just go and do something else."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 473160.0,
      "end_time": 476160.0,
      "text": "You know, switch topics, switch context,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 476400.0,
      "end_time": 477496.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ll forget the wrong answer"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 477520.0,
      "end_time": 481120.0,
      "text": "and that gives the right answer space to pop into the front of your mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 482800.0,
      "end_time": 485856.0,
      "text": "But on the slower timescale that interests me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 485880.0,
      "end_time": 487880.0,
      "text": "being stuck is a much more serious thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 488920.0,
      "end_time": 491400.0,
      "text": "You get turned down for funding."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 491760.0,
      "end_time": 495000.0,
      "text": "Your cell cultures won&#39;t grow, your rockets keep crashing."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 496000.0,
      "end_time": 499880.0,
      "text": "Nobody wants to publish you fantasy novel about a school for wizards."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 501400.0,
      "end_time": 505536.0,
      "text": "Or maybe you just can&#39;t find the solution to the problem that you&#39;re working on."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 505560.0,
      "end_time": 510296.0,
      "text": "And being stuck like that means stasis, stress,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 510320.0,
      "end_time": 512000.0,
      "text": "possibly even depression."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 513280.0,
      "end_time": 518456.0,
      "text": "But if you have another exciting, challenging project to work on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 518480.0,
      "end_time": 522616.0,
      "text": "being stuck on one is just an opportunity to do something else."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 522640.0,
      "end_time": 526616.0,
      "text": "We could all get stuck sometimes, even Albert Einstein."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 526640.0,
      "end_time": 531150.0,
      "text": "Ten years after the original, miraculous year that I described,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 531390.0,
      "end_time": 535976.0,
      "text": "Einstein was putting together the pieces of his theory of general relativity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 536000.0,
      "end_time": 537920.0,
      "text": "his greatest achievement."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 538680.0,
      "end_time": 540000.0,
      "text": "And he was exhausted."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 541800.0,
      "end_time": 543856.0,
      "text": "And so he turned to an easier problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 543880.0,
      "end_time": 547456.0,
      "text": "He proposed the stimulated emission of radiation."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 547480.0,
      "end_time": 552296.0,
      "text": "Which, as you may know, is the S in laser."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 552320.0,
      "end_time": 556816.0,
      "text": "So he&#39;s laying down the theoretical foundation for the laser beam,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 556840.0,
      "end_time": 558696.0,
      "text": "and then, while he&#39;s doing that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 558720.0,
      "end_time": 561936.0,
      "text": "he moves back to general relativity, and he&#39;s refreshed."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 561960.0,
      "end_time": 565296.0,
      "text": "He sees what the theory implies --"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 565320.0,
      "end_time": 568656.0,
      "text": "that the universe isn&#39;t static."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 568680.0,
      "end_time": 570295.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s expanding."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 570320.0,
      "end_time": 572416.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s an idea so staggering,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 572440.0,
      "end_time": 576360.0,
      "text": "Einstein can&#39;t bring himself to believe it for years."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 577680.0,
      "end_time": 579976.0,
      "text": "Look, if you get stuck"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 580000.0,
      "end_time": 584440.0,
      "text": "and you get the ball rolling on laser beams,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 585520.0,
      "end_time": 586976.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re in pretty good shape."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 587000.0,
      "end_time": 588976.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 589000.0,
      "end_time": 592496.0,
      "text": "So, that&#39;s the case for slow-motion multitasking."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 592520.0,
      "end_time": 595536.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m not promising that it&#39;s going to turn you into Einstein."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 595560.0,
      "end_time": 598776.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not even promising it&#39;s going to turn you into Michael Crichton."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 598800.0,
      "end_time": 601760.0,
      "text": "But it is a powerful way to organize our creative lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 603240.0,
      "end_time": 604720.0,
      "text": "But there&#39;s a problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 606360.0,
      "end_time": 611440.0,
      "text": "How do we stop all of these projects becoming completely overwhelming?"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 612520.0,
      "end_time": 616000.0,
      "text": "How do we keep all these ideas straight in our minds?"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 616920.0,
      "end_time": 620896.0,
      "text": "Well, here&#39;s a simple solution, a practical solution"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 620920.0,
      "end_time": 624415.0,
      "text": "from the great American choreographer, Twyla Tharp."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 624440.0,
      "end_time": 626216.0,
      "text": "Over the last few decades,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 626240.0,
      "end_time": 630736.0,
      "text": "she&#39;s blurred boundaries, mixed genres, won prizes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 630760.0,
      "end_time": 635536.0,
      "text": "danced to the music of everybody, from Philip Glass to Billy Joel."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 635560.0,
      "end_time": 637136.0,
      "text": "She&#39;s written three books."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 637160.0,
      "end_time": 640439.0,
      "text": "I mean, she&#39;s a slow-motion multitasker, of course she is."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 641800.0,
      "end_time": 645815.0,
      "text": "She says, \"You have to be all things."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 645840.0,
      "end_time": 647456.0,
      "text": "Why exclude?"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 647480.0,
      "end_time": 650400.0,
      "text": "You have to be everything.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 651240.0,
      "end_time": 653616.0,
      "text": "And Tharp&#39;s method"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 653640.0,
      "end_time": 657976.0,
      "text": "for preventing all of these different projects from becoming overwhelming"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 658000.0,
      "end_time": 659296.0,
      "text": "is a simple one."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 659320.0,
      "end_time": 661856.0,
      "text": "She gives each project a big cardboard box,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 661880.0,
      "end_time": 664576.0,
      "text": "writes the name of the project on the side of the box."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 664600.0,
      "end_time": 669160.0,
      "text": "And into it, she tosses DVDs and books, magazine cuttings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 669400.0,
      "end_time": 671160.0,
      "text": "theater programs, physical objects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 671400.0,
      "end_time": 676160.0,
      "text": "really anything that&#39;s provided a source of creative inspiration."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 676400.0,
      "end_time": 677776.0,
      "text": "And she writes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 677800.0,
      "end_time": 682400.0,
      "text": "\"The box means I never have to worry about forgetting."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 682880.0,
      "end_time": 685816.0,
      "text": "One of the biggest fears for a creative person"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 685840.0,
      "end_time": 688296.0,
      "text": "is that some brilliant idea will get lost"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 688320.0,
      "end_time": 691800.0,
      "text": "because you didn&#39;t write it down and put it in a safe place."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 692920.0,
      "end_time": 694695.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t worry about that."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 694720.0,
      "end_time": 697800.0,
      "text": "Because I know where to find it."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 698160.0,
      "end_time": 699640.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s all in the box.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 701480.0,
      "end_time": 703616.0,
      "text": "You can manage many ideas like this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 703640.0,
      "end_time": 708295.0,
      "text": "either in physical boxes or in their digital equivalents."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 708320.0,
      "end_time": 710576.0,
      "text": "So, I would like to urge you"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 710600.0,
      "end_time": 713920.0,
      "text": "to embrace the art of slow-motion multitasking."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 714720.0,
      "end_time": 716776.0,
      "text": "Not because you&#39;re in a hurry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 716800.0,
      "end_time": 719839.0,
      "text": "but because you&#39;re in no hurry at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 721360.0,
      "end_time": 724560.0,
      "text": "And I want to give you one final example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 724800.0,
      "end_time": 726216.0,
      "text": "my favorite example."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 726240.0,
      "end_time": 727440.0,
      "text": "Charles Darwin."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 728200.0,
      "end_time": 732896.0,
      "text": "A man whose slow-burning multitasking is so staggering,"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 732920.0,
      "end_time": 736960.0,
      "text": "I need a diagram to explain it all to you."
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 736120.0,
      "end_time": 738456.0,
      "text": "We know what Darwin was doing at different times,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 738480.0,
      "end_time": 742176.0,
      "text": "because the creativity researchers Howard Gruber and Sara Davis"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 742200.0,
      "end_time": 745960.0,
      "text": "have analyzed his diaries and his notebooks."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 745120.0,
      "end_time": 747696.0,
      "text": "So, when he left school, age of 18,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 747720.0,
      "end_time": 750336.0,
      "text": "he was initially interested in two fields,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 750360.0,
      "end_time": 753616.0,
      "text": "zoology and geology."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 753640.0,
      "end_time": 758960.0,
      "text": "Pretty soon, he signed up to be the onboard naturalist on the \"Beagle.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 758120.0,
      "end_time": 760936.0,
      "text": "This is the ship that eventually took five years"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 760960.0,
      "end_time": 764456.0,
      "text": "to sail all the way around the southern oceans of the Earth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 764480.0,
      "end_time": 767296.0,
      "text": "stopping at the Galápagos, passing through the Indian ocean."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 767320.0,
      "end_time": 770296.0,
      "text": "While he was on the \"Beagle,\" he began researching coral reefs."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 770320.0,
      "end_time": 773576.0,
      "text": "This is a great synergy between his two interests"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 773600.0,
      "end_time": 775960.0,
      "text": "in zoology and geology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 775120.0,
      "end_time": 779600.0,
      "text": "and it starts to get him thinking about slow processes."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 780720.0,
      "end_time": 783496.0,
      "text": "But when he gets back from the voyage,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 783520.0,
      "end_time": 788175.0,
      "text": "his interests start to expand even further: psychology, botany;"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 788200.0,
      "end_time": 789536.0,
      "text": "for the rest of his life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 789560.0,
      "end_time": 793175.0,
      "text": "he&#39;s moving backwards and forwards between these different fields."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 793200.0,
      "end_time": 796560.0,
      "text": "He never quite abandons any of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 796800.0,
      "end_time": 799976.0,
      "text": "In 1837, he begins work on two very interesting projects."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 800000.0,
      "end_time": 802816.0,
      "text": "One of them: earthworms."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 802840.0,
      "end_time": 806416.0,
      "text": "The other, a little notebook which he titles"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 806440.0,
      "end_time": 809336.0,
      "text": "\"The transmutation of species.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 809360.0,
      "end_time": 815296.0,
      "text": "Then, Darwin starts studying my field, economics."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 815320.0,
      "end_time": 820176.0,
      "text": "He reads a book by the economist Thomas Malthus."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 820200.0,
      "end_time": 822416.0,
      "text": "And he has his eureka moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 822440.0,
      "end_time": 827976.0,
      "text": "In a flash, he realizes how species could emerge and evolve slowly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 828000.0,
      "end_time": 831560.0,
      "text": "through this process of the survival of the fittest."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 831800.0,
      "end_time": 833376.0,
      "text": "It all comes to him, he writes it all down,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 833400.0,
      "end_time": 837136.0,
      "text": "every single important element of the theory of evolution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 837160.0,
      "end_time": 838896.0,
      "text": "in that notebook."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 838920.0,
      "end_time": 842736.0,
      "text": "But then, a new project."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 842760.0,
      "end_time": 844360.0,
      "text": "His son William is born."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 845200.0,
      "end_time": 847896.0,
      "text": "Well, there&#39;s a natural experiment right there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 847920.0,
      "end_time": 850496.0,
      "text": "you get to observe the development of a human infant."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 850520.0,
      "end_time": 853216.0,
      "text": "So immediately, Darwin starts making notes."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 853240.0,
      "end_time": 856136.0,
      "text": "Now, of course, he&#39;s still working on the theory of evolution"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 856160.0,
      "end_time": 859160.0,
      "text": "and the development of the human infant."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 859400.0,
      "end_time": 860456.0,
      "text": "But during all of this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 860480.0,
      "end_time": 864656.0,
      "text": "he realizes he doesn&#39;t really know enough about taxonomy."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 864680.0,
      "end_time": 866415.0,
      "text": "So he starts studying that."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 866440.0,
      "end_time": 872896.0,
      "text": "And in the end, he spends eight years becoming the world&#39;s leading expert"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 872920.0,
      "end_time": 874360.0,
      "text": "on barnacles."
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 875320.0,
      "end_time": 877416.0,
      "text": "Then, \"Natural Selection.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 877440.0,
      "end_time": 882576.0,
      "text": "A book that he&#39;s to continue working on for his entire life, he never finishes it."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 882600.0,
      "end_time": 885456.0,
      "text": "\"Origin of Species\" is finally published"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 885480.0,
      "end_time": 889456.0,
      "text": "20 years after Darwin set out all the basic elements."
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 889480.0,
      "end_time": 892376.0,
      "text": "Then, the \"Descent of Man,\" controversial book."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 892400.0,
      "end_time": 896256.0,
      "text": "And then, the book about the development of the human infant."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 896280.0,
      "end_time": 900415.0,
      "text": "The one that was inspired when he could see his son, William,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 900440.0,
      "end_time": 903616.0,
      "text": "crawling on the sitting room floor in front of him."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 903640.0,
      "end_time": 907640.0,
      "text": "When the book was published, William was 37 years old."
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 908640.0,
      "end_time": 910856.0,
      "text": "And all this time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 910880.0,
      "end_time": 913856.0,
      "text": "Darwin&#39;s working on earthworms."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 913880.0,
      "end_time": 919856.0,
      "text": "He fills his billiard room with earthworms in pots, with glass covers."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 919880.0,
      "end_time": 922576.0,
      "text": "He shines lights on them, to see if they&#39;ll respond."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 922600.0,
      "end_time": 925456.0,
      "text": "He holds a hot poker next to them, to see if they move away."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 925480.0,
      "end_time": 927296.0,
      "text": "He chews tobacco and --"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 927320.0,
      "end_time": 928536.0,
      "text": "(Blows)"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 928560.0,
      "end_time": 931575.0,
      "text": "He blows on the earthworms to see if they have a sense of smell."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 931600.0,
      "end_time": 934880.0,
      "text": "He even plays the bassoon at the earthworms."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 936200.0,
      "end_time": 938896.0,
      "text": "I like to think of this great man"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 938920.0,
      "end_time": 941376.0,
      "text": "when he&#39;s tired, he&#39;s stressed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 941400.0,
      "end_time": 945415.0,
      "text": "he&#39;s anxious about the reception of his book \"The Descent of Man.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 945440.0,
      "end_time": 949520.0,
      "text": "You or I might log into Facebook or turn on the television."
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 950440.0,
      "end_time": 954256.0,
      "text": "Darwin would go into the billiard room to relax"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 954280.0,
      "end_time": 957360.0,
      "text": "by studying the earthworms intensely."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 958960.0,
      "end_time": 962856.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s why it&#39;s appropriate that one of his last great works"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 962880.0,
      "end_time": 967896.0,
      "text": "is the \"Formation of Vegetable Mould Through The Action of Worms.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 967920.0,
      "end_time": 969256.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 969280.0,
      "end_time": 974400.0,
      "text": "He worked upon that book for 44 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 976800.0,
      "end_time": 978776.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t live in the 19th century anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 978800.0,
      "end_time": 981136.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t think any of us could sit"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 981160.0,
      "end_time": 985280.0,
      "text": "on our creative or scientific projects for 44 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 986280.0,
      "end_time": 990616.0,
      "text": "But we do have something to learn from the great slow-motion multitaskers."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 990640.0,
      "end_time": 996000.0,
      "text": "From Einstein and Darwin to Michael Crichton and Twyla Tharp."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 997400.0,
      "end_time": 1000856.0,
      "text": "The modern world seems to present us with a choice."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 1000880.0,
      "end_time": 1004896.0,
      "text": "If we&#39;re not going to fast-twitch from browser window to browser window,"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 1004920.0,
      "end_time": 1006536.0,
      "text": "we have to live like a hermit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 1006560.0,
      "end_time": 1009880.0,
      "text": "focus on one thing to the exclusion of everything else."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 1010680.0,
      "end_time": 1013550.0,
      "text": "I think that&#39;s a false dilemma."
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 1013800.0,
      "end_time": 1015736.0,
      "text": "We can make multitasking work for us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 1015760.0,
      "end_time": 1018319.0,
      "text": "unleashing our natural creativity."
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 1019440.0,
      "end_time": 1020920.0,
      "text": "We just need to slow it down."
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 1022200.0,
      "end_time": 1023440.0,
      "text": "So ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 1024880.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1027376.0000000001,
      "text": "Make a list of your projects."
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 1027400.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1028800.0000000001,
      "text": "Put down your phone."
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 1029640.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1031680.0000000001,
      "text": "Pick up a couple of cardboard boxes."
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 1032880.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1034800.0000000001,
      "text": "And get to work."
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 1035240.0,
      "end_time": 1036616.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 1036640.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1040480.0000000001,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}